OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1779865531
OL,3,CFour hundred attend protest over
OL,4,Cfuture of road washed away by storms
OL,6,FHundreds of people have walked the
OL,7,FSlapton Line in South Devon in protest
OL,8,Fthat an A-road connecting remote towns
OL,9,Fremains unusable four months after it
OL,10,Fcollapsed.
OL,12,FPart of the A379 at Torcross was
OL,13,Fwashed away after sea defences were
OL,14,Fdamaged during January's storms.
OL,16,FThousands of people have since signed
OL,17,Fa petition created by local MP
OL,18,FCaroline Voaden calling for the road
OL,19,Fto be repaired.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
