OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1779865531
OL,3,CFour hundred attend protest over
OL,4,Cfuture of road washed away by storms
OL,6,FThe protest, attended by more than 400
OL,7,Fpeople, was organised by local parish
OL,8,Fcouncillors who warn the road's
OL,9,Fclosure means people are struggling to
OL,10,Fget to work, school and appointments.
OL,12,FThey said local businesses are also
OL,13,Flosing out on customers, with some
OL,14,Freporting a 25% loss in revenue.
OL,16,FDetours caused by the closure can take
OL,17,Fupwards of 45 minutes along country
OL,18,Froads unsuited for large volumes of
OL,19,Ftraffic.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1779865531
OL,3,CFour hundred attend protest over
OL,4,Cfuture of road washed away by storms
OL,6,F"Four months on there's still no
OL,7,Fsolution to fixing our road and
OL,8,Fthere's no funding commitment," said
OL,9,Fparish councillor Paul Green.
OL,11,F"We're feeling ignored, people don't
OL,12,Fseem to be listening to local people
OL,13,Fat a local level about local problems."
OL,15,FJulian Brazil, leader of Devon County
OL,16,FCouncil, previously warned that locals
OL,17,Fwould have to be "realistic" about the
OL,18,Ffuture of the coastal road.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
