FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1779865531
OL,3,CFour hundred attend protest over
OL,4,Cfuture of road washed away by storms
OL,6,FEstimates suggest repairing the A379 -
OL,7,Fwhich also required repairs after
OL,8,Fstorms in 2001 and 2018 - could cost
OL,9,Ftens of millions of pounds.
OL,11,FThe road is built on unstable shingle,
OL,12,Fand climate change experts have warned
OL,13,Fthat as sea levels rise the threat to
OL,14,Fthe A379 from storms will increase.
OL,16,FThe government said it is providing
OL,17,F#450million for road maintenance in
OL,18,Fthe South Devon area over the next
OL,19,Ffour years.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
