OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1779865531
OL,3,CFour hundred attend protest over
OL,4,Cfuture of road washed away by storms
OL,6,FBut protestors say the road is
OL,7,Fessential for those living in the area.
OL,9,F"I'm fighting for this road because
OL,10,Fit's part of our heritage, part of our
OL,11,Flife, and it keeps communities
OL,12,Ftogether," one protestor told ITV West
OL,13,FCountry.
OL,15,F"Without this road communities will
OL,16,Fdisappear, and we can't have that."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
